From 1d7712419fc5f4c8af9c7905e6f17e183febf472 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "lakshmipathi.ganapathi" <laks@neverbreak.ai>
Date: Sun, 22 Mar 2026 13:35:26 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] Print csum for a given file on stdout with subvolume support

Add 'btrfs inspect-internal dump-csum' command that prints BTRFS
checksums for a given file. Uses BTRFS_IOC_INO_LOOKUP ioctl to
resolve the correct subvolume root, fixing the previous limitation
where files inside subvolumes produced empty output.

Signed-off-by: Lakshmipathi Ganapathi <lakshmipathi.g@gmail.com>
